ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectWaywayseecappo First Nation 1881 Surrender Specific Claim Settlement Agreement
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations to execute, on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada, the WAYWAYSEECAPPO FIRST NATION 1881 SURRENDER SPECIFIC CLAIM SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between Canada and the First Nation; and (2) accepting the absolute surrender to Canada of all rights and interests of the lands.
